dct_title_s: A map of New England and New York
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Also covers N.J. From John Speed's Theatre of the empire of Great Britain. Text on verso. Includes ill. of animals and coat of arms. Shows names of Indian tribes.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Sold by Tho. Basset in Fleet Street and Richard Chiswell in St. Paul's Church Yard, [1676]
